{"tid":1984591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀: 港台節目認知率及收視率低 梁家榮沒有盡責教育下屬","createTime":"2020-04-22T14:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T07:41:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a96d72f1d46bb65a82ca119bdbd99affd57c60eb","tid":1984591,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:14:47.000Z","msg":"立法會恢復二讀辯論《撥款條例草案》，民主黨議員黃碧雲傍晚一度提出點算法定人數。<br />\n<br />\n新民黨主席葉劉淑儀發言時說，香港電台偏離約章，當局早就應檢討香港電台運作，她又說，港台最近訪問世衛官員有關疫情問題，但提問具政治性，反映廣播處長梁家榮並無教導僱員，提升他們了解國家及一國兩制、培養他們公民及國民身分認同感，認為梁家榮管理失敗。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀說，香港電台的公共事務及一般製作開支超高，當中包括製作有關嘻笑怒罵節目，港台流動應用程式的節目瀏覽率亦下跌、收視率低，認為應從衡工量值和管理方面檢討運作。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，政府的功能是提供市場不能提供的服務，關注香港電台應否繼續發揮商界、私人電台或電視台能達致的作用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522128-20200422.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522128-20200422.htm&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=8918d5b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522128-20200422.htm&h=63d9fa84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522128-20200422.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5625cc88abe4b1b076881290dd2524c17c01eea5","tid":1984591,"uid":107577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Twitter 國際戰線需要你<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\nTwitter文宣組<br />\n戰線台 @twittermansyunzou <br />\n<br />\nReddit戰線 @reddithk_channel<br />\n文宣 @hkstandstrong_promo_int @guardiansofhongkong<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=ac2ccfdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n做任務，推任務，整圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cm4FxNr.jpg\" data-thumbnai